Chorrolis rise from the ranks of capable, usually</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>greedy merchan=
ts.
Some ply their trade from market stalls in Bartertown,</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>while others s=
atisfy
their desire to imitate Chorrolis by</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>traveling acro=
ss
Barsaive in trade caravans.</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Chorrolis freq=
uently
inspires his questors to acquire specific</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>objects that he
treasures. Widely known for their unbeatable bargaining</p>

