<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Also, the char=
acter
must use the Horror’s Spell Defense as the Difficulty</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Number for his
Thread Weaving attempt, not the falseman’s.</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Some Horrors s=
