hey
cannot imagine that the Universe actually gave</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>birth to somet=
hing
so hideous—and the molgrim is certainly hideous,</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>combining bits=
 and
pieces of many different creatures into a</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>truly sickening
whole. Moderately sized, the thing is about as tall as</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>a large bear, =
but
much broader, with a deep and powerful chest. Its</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>back slopes li=
ke a
