<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>as a human’s=
 arms,
and the three fingers on its broad hands are tipped</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>with claws as =
long
