<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Even though it=
 looks
like a large and ugly frog, the molgrim is not</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>an amphibian. =
Its
hide is not moist like a frog’s, but dry and tough</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>like imperfect=
ly
cured leather. Short, thick, oily fur grows from its</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>mottled skin,
