<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>has a large be=
ak in
place of a snout. Wickedly hooked and sharp</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>as a dragon’=
s claws,
this beak is perfect for tearing flesh.</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>The molgrim is=
 a
carnivore, most often found in the foothills</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>of the rugged
