<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>both combatant=
s; one
gets torn to shreds, and the other dies soon</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>afterward from=
 its
wounds. The defending male first attempts to</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>charge the
challenging male and drive the challenger from his territory.</p>

