<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>males and fema=
les
joining multiple times with different partners.</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>After being
impregnated, the female remains underwater until</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>ready to lay h=
er egg
pouch. This rubbery, resilient sack is coated</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>with a sticky
