<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>try to take ac=
tion,
the Horror is consolidating its control over others</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>in local gover=
nment
and forcing them to commit horrible acts—the</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>characters mus=
t stop
the Horror before it destroys the entire city.</p>

