<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>around itself.=
 The
creature can lower the temperature so far that</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>the thin skin =
of
most Namegivers will freeze, and fingers and toes</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>grow brittle w=
ith
