Vasdenjas said this, I heard his stomach</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>growl), Taint =
is an
entity of which all Barsaive should be</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>made aware. I =
