Barsaive, being slow and stupid and meaty</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>enough to feed
several people. The modern-day vetta is still slow</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>and stupid, bu=
