harm. It seems to have gained this ability as it</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>lost every nat=
ural
defense it once had, which suggests that even</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Horror-tainted
creatures must bow to the essential harmony of</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>the Universe. =
