<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>decides to tak=
e a
long nap in the hot sun. The vettas amble away</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>from the drowsy
predator, which after a time slowly comes to its</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>senses. Because
