<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Tire Others: B=
ecause
the vettas’ Tire Others power depends</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>on their numbe=
rs,
