<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>into a herd of
vettas. They suddenly become extremely tired and</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>decide to have=
 a
quick little nap. Unfortunately for them, a pride</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>of stone lions=
 also
fell into the vettas’ trap. When the sun climbs</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>higher and the
vettas’ power wanes, the characters and the lions</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>begin to
awaken—very, very close to each other.</p>

