<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>rough cylinder=
 about
three feet wide and six feet high, but wingflayers</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>have been know=
n to
