<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Ysrthgrathe us=
ually
allows the victim to believe it might work before claiming both unfortunate
targets. Ysrthgrathe never willingly lets a victim escape and the Horror ad=
ores
trickery.</p>

